{"type":"text","timestamp":1784746444378,"sessionID":"ses_074e2c605ffeqnpXN031WqV2u2","part":{"id":"prt_f8b2d81820010XAVGbVm87hiWl","messageID":"msg_f8b2d7d87001oLLGCCwrRdTeYk","sessionID":"ses_074e2c605ffeqnpXN031WqV2u2","type":"text","text":"Implemented the core functionality for RemixHub:\n\n### Added Modules\n- **`trend_engine.py`**\n  - `TrendEngine` with deterministic `get_trends` method simulating behavior‑verified trend retrieval.\n- **`nlp_core.py`**\n  - `ContentGen` with deterministic `generate` method producing copy, hashtags, and visual prompts from a trend string.\n- **`dispatcher.py`**\n  - `SocialDispatcher` with `dispatch` method that simulates queuing a dispatch job.\n\n### Updated `main.py`\n- Imported the new modules and instantiated their services.\n- Replaced placeholder TODOs with real calls:\n  - `/trends` now returns trends from `TrendEngine`.\n  - `/generate` returns generated content from `ContentGen`.\n  - `/dispatch` returns dispatch status from `SocialDispatcher`.\n\nThese changes provide functional endpoints for the three core components, laying the groundwork for further integration with Kafka, Spark, PostgreSQL, OAuth2, and AWS services as the project evolves.","time":{"start":1784746443138,"end":1784746444375}}}
